'''Masha Heddle''' is a minor character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. She is played by guest star [[Susie Kelly]] and only appears in &quot;[[Cripples, Bastards and Broken Things]].&quot; Masha Heddle is the innkeeper at the busy and successful [[Crossroads Inn]].
